NK131(do)004:1: // boo ra s+t+ya apra&a&a&a ka ra apra&a&a&a h+n+aa n+aam sa
NK131(do)004:2: ma y+aa ny+tso t+ya s+ya pa ri h+aa r+aa ga
NK131(do)004:3: ma sh+tsa bi d+y+aa ya d+y+aa ru na n+aa m+aa
NK131(do)004:4: ste //// snga 'gyur rnying ma'i gzhung la brgal ba'i
NK131(do)004:5: lan lung dang rigs pa'i skya rengs dang po zhes
NK131(do)004:7: na mah dzi t+phu shaga&a&a&a la s+ya bu d+d+ha ya /
NK131(do)004:8: b+ai d+h+ram dz+ny+aa pa ri be d+ya ba sh+yi na ////
NK131(do)004:9: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK131(do)004:10: dri bral mkhyen pa shes bya kun gzigs nas ////
NK131(do)004:11: b+aa g+mi n+wi gra ha mo k+sha sa t+pa thoo /
NK131(do)004:12: sa m+bi ta s+ya su kri tihra&a&a b+h+r+aum s+phu tam /
NK131(do)004:13: she sh+ti rma sa ma ta tra bee na mah //
NK131(do)004:14: legs 'doms gsung gis lus can thar lam du //
NK131(do)004:15: dkri ba'i mdzad bzang srid pa'i mthar 'phro ba'i //
NK131(do)004:16: ston pa mtshungs med de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK131(do)004:17: rgyal kun gsung gi dbang phyug he ru kah grub brgya'i gtso bo 'dzam gling mdzes pa'i rgyan //
NK131(do)004:18: gangs ljongs bstan pa'i shing rta gcig pu pa //
NK131(do)004:19: o rgyan sangs rgyas gnyis pas dge legs stsol //
NK131(do)004:20: srid pa'i 'khri shing gcod la ches dpal pa'i //
NK131(do)004:21: mkhyen rab ral gri'i gnyen gcig lhag pa'i lha //
NK131(do)004:22: 'jam dpa'i dbyangs des bdag dang khyod kyi yang //
NK131(do)004:23: the tshom d+r+wa ba mtha' dag gcod par mdzod //
NK131(do)004:24: bsil ldan gangs ri'i ljongs 'di ru //
NK131(do)004:25: btsan po lha ri snyan shal nas //
NK131(do)004:26: mnga' bdag khri ral yan chad kyi //
NK131(do)004:27: chos rgyal rnams kyi sku ring la //
NK131(do)004:28: pan chen lha rig seng ge nas //
NK131(do)004:29: smri ti dz+ny+aa na'i bar dag dang //
NK131(do)004:30: lo ts+aa thu mi sam+b+ho nas //
NK131(do)004:31: chos kyi bzang po'i bar dag tu //
NK131(do)004:32: byon pa'i lo pan de rnams kyis //
NK131(do)004:33: bsgyur ba'i mdo rgyud dgongs 'grel bcas //
NK131(do)004:34: ji snyed bzhugs pa thams cad la //
NK131(do)004:35: snga 'gyur rnying ma zhes su grags //
NK131(do)004:36: dus de'i chos rgyal lo pan tshogs //
NK131(do)004:37: phal cher sa bcu'i dbang phyug tu //
NK131(do)004:38: tshad ma'i skyes bu'i lung bstan par //
NK131(do)004:39: tshad mas grub pa ma yin nam //
NK131(do)004:40: des na lung don rig pa yis //
NK131(do)004:41: rnam par dpyod pa'i blo ldan zhing //
NK131(do)004:42: gzu bor gnas pa'i gang zag rnams //
NK131(do)004:43: lugs der the tshom za mi srid //
NK131(do)004:44: 'on kyang blo mthu zhan pa dang //
NK131(do)004:45: mi dge'i bshes kyi zin pa dang //
NK131(do)004:46: phyogs lhung gdon gyis gtses pa rnams //
NK131(do)004:47: the tshom log ltas bcing bar snang //
NK131(do)004:48: de lta na yang khyed cag gis //
NK131(do)004:49: ltar snang sgro skur tsam min par //
NK131(do)004:50: yang dag lung dang rig pa yis //
NK131(do)004:51: rnying gzhung log par sgrub mi nus //
NK131(do)004:52: ci phyir zhe na gzhung de kun //
NK131(do)004:53: gal te log pa nyid yin na //
NK131(do)004:54: 'dul ba sher phyin dkon brtsegs dang //
NK131(do)004:55: phal chen la sogs mdo phyogs dang //
NK131(do)004:56: rnam 'joms don zhags mtshan brjod dang //
NK131(do)004:57: rnam snang mngon byang rgyud la sogs //
NK131(do)004:58: sngags phyogs de dag dgongs 'grel bcas //
NK131(do)004:59: bka' dang bstan bcos phal che ba //
NK131(do)004:60: rnying ma'i lo pan gyis bsgyur phyir //
NK131(do)004:61: khyod la log pa'i chos su 'gyur //
NK131(do)004:62: de lta na ni gangs ljongs 'dir //
NK131(do)004:63: yang dag chos kyi skal pa phra //
NK131(do)004:64: gal te mdo dang phyi rgyud sogs //
NK131(do)004:65: de rnams log pa ma yin kyang //
NK131(do)004:66: rnying ma'i bla med rgyud sde rnams //
NK131(do)004:67: log pa yin zhes smra na ni //
NK131(do)004:68: mnyam sbyor zla gsang thig le dang //
NK131(do)004:69: gsang 'dus phur pa rtsa dum sogs //
NK131(do)004:70: tshad ma'i rgyud sde de rnams kyang //
NK131(do)004:71: rnam dag min par thal bar 'gyur //
NK131(do)004:72: de kun snga 'gyur yin pa'i phyir //
NK131(do)004:73: 'dod na gsang sngags gsar ma yang //
NK131(do)004:74: yang dag min par thal 'gyur te //
NK131(do)004:75: gsar ma la yang de yod phyir //
NK131(do)004:76: gal te snga 'gyur rnying ma yi //
NK131(do)004:77: mdo phyogs kun dang gsang sngags kyis //
NK131(do)004:78: phyi nang rgyud sde phal che ba //
NK131(do)004:79: yang dag nyid du khas len cing //
NK131(do)004:81: sems klong man ngag sde sogs kyi //
NK131(do)004:82: rgyud sde kha cig chos log tu //
NK131(do)004:83: 'dod ces khyed cag smra na ni //
NK131(do)004:84: sgyur byed lo pan gcig nyid kyis //
NK131(do)004:85: bsgyur ba'i mdo rgyud la la zhig /
NK131(do)004:86: dag cing la la ma dag pa'i //
NK131(do)004:87: gtam 'di sdang zhugs tsam zhig las //
NK131(do)004:88: rig pas 'thad pa ma grub kyang //
NK131(do)004:89: ci ste gal gyis 'chu byed na //
NK131(do)004:91: rnam dag gtan tshigs ci zhig yod //
NK131(do)004:92: 'di ltar sdeb sbyor nyams pa dang //
NK131(do)004:93: legs sbyar skad dang mi mthun cing //
NK131(do)004:94: grong gi skad dang 'dres sogs kyis //
NK131(do)004:95: rnam dag min par 'dod ce na //
NK131(do)004:96: phyogs lnga'i rgyud sde phal cher la //
NK131(do)004:97: rtags 'di ma grub kha cig la //
NK131(do)004:98: grub kyang de yis chos min par //
NK131(do)004:99: thal ba'i khyab pa sgrub mi nus //
NK131(do)004:100: de yis rgyu mtshan dus 'khor dang //
NK131(do)004:101: phyag chen thig le'i rgyud sogs nas //
NK131(do)004:102: gsal bar bshad pa ma mthong ngam //
NK131(do)004:103: dus phyis rgya gar yul gru 'ga' //
NK131(do)004:104: yongs su grags pa med pa dang //
NK131(do)004:105: gsar ma'i lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis //
NK131(do)004:106: mthong thos med pa'i phyir zhe na //
NK131(do)004:107: de la khyab ba ma grub ste //
NK131(do)004:108: sangs rgyas 'das nas lo grangs ni //
NK131(do)004:109: brgya lhag tsam du theg chen gzhung //
NK131(do)004:110: yongs su grags par ma gyur dang //
NK131(do)004:111: deng sang tsam na'ang 'phags yul na //
NK131(do)004:112: sde snod gsum sogs rgyal ba'i bka' //
NK131(do)004:113: yod pa'i nges pa ma mchis kyang //
NK131(do)004:114: med pa tsam gyis ma dag par //
NK131(do)004:115: sgrub pa mkhas pa'i gzhung lugs bzhin //
NK131(do)004:116: lo ts+aa 'ga' yis ma mthong ba //
NK131(do)004:117: gtan tshigs nyid du mi che ste //
NK131(do)004:118: b+ham ga la yi rgyal po'i sras //
NK131(do)004:119: yongs su rdzogs pa'i pan+di ta //
NK131(do)004:120: grub pa'i sa mthor gshegs gyur pa //
NK131(do)004:121: lha gcig d+ai pam ka ra ste //
NK131(do)004:122: des kyang sngon chad ma gzigs pa'i //
NK131(do)004:123: rgyud sde du ma bsam yas kyi //
NK131(do)004:124: rgya dpe'i khrod nas gzigs so zhes //
NK131(do)004:125: jo bo'i rnam thar nyid du gsal //
NK131(do)004:126: ma mthong med pa ma yin zhes //
NK131(do)004:127: gsungs pa deng 'dir dran par byos //
NK131(do)004:129: mkhas pa mang ba'i rtsod bcas su //
NK131(do)004:130: mdzad phyir rnam dag min ce na //
NK131(do)004:131: der yang khyab pa ma grub ste //
NK131(do)004:132: sangs rgyas pa la mu stegs rtsod //
NK131(do)004:133: theg chen gzhung la nyan thos rtsod //
NK131(do)004:134: bye mdo sems tsam dbu ma sogs //
NK131(do)004:135: grub mtha' phan tshun ma rtsod med //
NK131(do)004:136: gsar ma pa'ang nang tshan gyis //
NK131(do)004:137: phan tshun thams cad rtsod bcas phyir //
NK131(do)004:138: kun kyang log pa yin nam ci //
NK131(do)004:139: dpal ldan dus kyi 'khor lo dang //
NK131(do)004:140: lam 'bras zhi byed gcod la sogs //
NK131(do)004:141: rgyud dang man ngag snyan rgyud chos //
NK131(do)004:142: phal cher rtsod bcas kho na'i phyir //
NK131(do)004:143: de kun dor byar gyur pa na //
NK131(do)004:144: ha cang nyid du ma thal lam //
NK131(do)004:146: rgya 'grel zur tsam med do lo'i //
NK131(do)004:147: gtan tshigs ltar snang tsam bkod kyang //
NK131(do)004:148: de ni ma nges rtag yin pas //
NK131(do)004:149: tshul des 'gog par ga la nus //
NK131(do)004:151: chos dang chos min dbye ba ni //
NK131(do)004:152: blo gros phur khung thug pa'i gtam //
NK131(do)004:153: de ltar na'ang rnying rgyud phal //
NK131(do)004:154: 'gyur byang yod pa sha stag ste //
NK131(do)004:155: sems sde snga 'gyur bee ro dang //
NK131(do)004:156: phyi 'byung bi ma la yis bsgyur //
NK131(do)004:157: klong sde'i skor rnams sh+r+ai seng dang //
NK131(do)004:158: bee ro g.yu sgra sogs kyis bsgyur //
NK131(do)004:159: man ngag sde yi rgyud bcu bdun //
NK131(do)004:160: bi ma ska cog nyang sogs kyis //
NK131(do)004:161: bsgyur zhing gzhan yang mdo sgyu sogs //
NK131(do)004:162: 'gyur byang rang rang gsham na gsal //
NK131(do)004:164: ma dag nyid du 'dod mi nus //
NK131(do)004:165: dkon mchog rjes dran mdo dang ni //
NK131(do)004:166: s+aa lu ljang ba'i mdo la sogs //
NK131(do)004:168: de dag rnam dag min par ni //
NK131(do)004:169: dpyod ldan sum kyang smra mi spobs //
NK131(do)004:170: de phyir bag yod mdzad na legs //
NK131(do)004:171: 'grel pa med pa'ang rtags ma grub //
NK131(do)004:172: rgyud rgyal gsang ba snying po la //
NK131(do)004:173: rgya 'grel rim gnyis spar khab dang //
NK131(do)004:175: rgya cher 'grel sogs du ma dang //
NK131(do)004:176: dga' rab b+ai ma la gnyis kyi //
NK131(do)004:177: mtshan brjod rdzogs pa chen po ru //
NK131(do)004:178: bkral ba'i 'grel pa rnam gnyis dang //
NK131(do)004:179: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi //
NK131(do)004:180: 'grel pa rdo la gser zhun dang //
NK131(do)004:181: slob dpon pad+ma sam b+h+aa wa'i //
NK131(do)004:182: man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba sogs //
NK131(do)004:183: bka' gter 'grel pa mtha' yas pa //
NK131(do)004:184: deng sang dus na'ang bzhugs pa mang //
NK131(do)004:185: gzhan yang bcu gdun rgyud sogs la //
NK131(do)004:187: deng sang dpe rgyun dkon pa tsam //
NK131(do)004:188: mtshan rnams rnying ma'i gzhung na yod //
NK131(do)004:189: 'grel pa med pas ma dag par //
NK131(do)004:190: 'jog na dkon brtsegs phal chen sogs //
NK131(do)004:191: mdo rgyud mang zhig cir 'gyur am //
NK131(do)004:192: de rnams phyis pa'i dgag tshul dngos //
NK131(do)004:193: yin min dpyod ldan rnams kyis ltos //
NK131(do)004:194: 'gyur tshul bris kyang de dag la //
NK131(do)004:195: bsgyur ba'i dpang po med ce na //
NK131(do)004:196: lung zin sprul pa'i chos rgyal gyi //
NK131(do)004:197: bzhugs gnas chos 'khor rnam pa gsum //
NK131(do)004:198: lugs gnyis khrims kyi bka' btsan zhing //
NK131(do)004:199: mkhas pa'i skye bos gang ba'i yul //
NK131(do)004:200: bsgyur gzhi gnas kyi dpang po yin //
NK131(do)004:201: mdo dang rgyud sde du ma nas //
NK131(do)004:202: rgyal ba'i lung gis basngagasa mdzad cing //
NK131(do)004:203: mi rabs du mar bzhugs pa dang //
NK131(do)004:204: dngos snang sgyu mar ston nus pa'i //
NK131(do)004:206: 'phags yul pan chen brgya rtsa dang //
NK131(do)004:207: skad rigs sum brgya drug cu la //
NK131(do)004:208: mkhas shing gnas yul bsgrod nus pa'i //
NK131(do)004:209: grub brnyes lo ts+aa brgya rtsa sogs //
NK131(do)004:210: sgyur byed gang zag dpang po yin //
NK131(do)004:211: de rnams dpang du mi che na //
NK131(do)004:212: rgyal rigs rgyal sa ma zin par //
NK131(do)004:213: mtha' la 'khyar pa'i sbyin bdag dang //
NK131(do)004:214: mtha' 'khob yam bu'i grong khyer sogs //
NK131(do)004:215: blun pos bsten pa'i yul rnams dang //
NK131(do)004:218: lo ts+aa'i ming btags phal cher zhig /
NK131(do)004:219: dpang po nyid du ji ltar 'os //
NK131(do)004:220: mdzub mo brang la tshugs la soms //
NK131(do)004:221: dpal 'dzin dmyal bar song ba yang //
NK131(do)004:222: tshad ma'i sgrub byed min no skad //
NK131(do)004:223: rdzogs sangs rgyas la sdang ba yis //
NK131(do)004:224: lhas byin dmyal bar song ba dang //
NK131(do)004:225: theg chen chos la skur btab pas //
NK131(do)004:226: nyan thos lnga brgya gnas ngan du //
NK131(do)004:227: lhung bar mdo las bshad pa rnams //
NK131(do)004:228: sangs rgyas dang ni theg chen gzhung //
NK131(do)004:229: gnyen po'i yul du grub pa yi //
NK131(do)004:230: che ba bstan phyir ma yin nam //
NK131(do)004:232: snga 'gyur gzhug la skur btab nas //
NK131(do)004:233: rdo rje'i dmyal bar gshegs pa des //
NK131(do)004:234: gzhung 'di rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang //
NK131(do)004:235: mtshungs pa nyid du yang dag grub //
NK131(do)004:236: de phyir sgrub byed tshad ma yin //
NK131(do)004:237: dpal 'dzin nyid kyis sbyar ba yin //
NK131(do)004:238: gzhung de da dung 'dug go lo //
NK131(do)004:239: gzhung de'i brjod bya lung rig gis //
NK131(do)004:240: tshar gcad zin pa des gas chog /
NK131(do)004:241: gzhung nyid med 'gro ga la dgos //
NK131(do)004:242: gzhan du mu stegs pas sbyar ba'i //
NK131(do)004:243: dbang phyug nag po'i rgyud dang ni //
NK131(do)004:244: dbyu gu gsum pa'i gzhung la sogs //
NK131(do)004:245: da dung yod cing de dag la //
NK131(do)004:246: tshad mar byed pa'i mu stegs pa //
NK131(do)004:247: rab tu mang pa'ang yod pa'i phyir //
NK131(do)004:248: phyogs glang chos kyi grags pa sogs //
NK131(do)004:249: rig pa'i dbang phyug de rnams kyis //
NK131(do)004:250: tshar ma chod ces smra'am ci //
NK131(do)004:251: des na de 'dra'i gzhung lugs dang //
NK131(do)004:252: yod kyang log par rtog pa'i srog /
NK131(do)004:253: rig pa'i mtshon gyis bcad zin pas //
NK131(do)004:254: gzhung lugs shi ba'i ro yin no //
NK131(do)004:255: mdor na de dang de 'dra ba'i //
NK131(do)004:256: rnying gzhung 'gog pa'i rim pa rnams //
NK131(do)004:257: 'gal dang ma khyab khyab ches pa'i //
NK131(do)004:258: skyon gyi phung por gyur ba mang //
NK131(do)004:259: nges par chos dang chos min gyi //
NK131(do)004:260: rnam dbye legs par phye 'dod na //
NK131(do)004:261: rgyal ba nyid kyis rjes gnang zhing //
NK131(do)004:262: rgya bod mkhas pas bzhed pa yi //
NK131(do)004:263: brtags pa gsum dang rton pa bzhi //
NK131(do)004:264: bka' rtags phyag rgya rnam bzhi dang //
NK131(do)004:265: dngos sam brgyud nas dug gsum gyi //
NK131(do)004:267: tshul gsum ldan pa'i tshad ma yi //
NK131(do)004:268: rig pas zhib tu brtag dgos so //
NK131(do)004:269: de ltar legs par brtags pa na //
NK131(do)004:270: rnying ma'i gzhung lugs 'khrul med rnams //
NK131(do)004:271: bsreg bcad brdar ba'i gser zhun bzhin //
NK131(do)004:272: lhag par mdzes kyis gzhan du min //
NK131(do)004:273: de yi thad nas phyis gyur pa'i //
NK131(do)004:274: gzhung lugs phal cher snag cha'i yug /
NK131(do)004:275: bzhag pa ji bzhin gzod mthong 'gyur //
NK131(do)004:276: 'dir ni gsar du sgrub mi dgos //
NK131(do)004:277: sngon byon mkhas pa'i mkhas pa mchog /
NK131(do)004:278: rong zom chos kyi bzang po dang //
NK131(do)004:279: rog ston shes rab 'od zer dang //
NK131(do)004:280: mkhas pa thang ston lo ts+aa ba //
NK131(do)004:281: kun mkhyen bsam yas pa sogs kyis //
NK131(do)004:282: snga 'gyur bkar sgrub mdzad pa yod //
NK131(do)004:283: gzhan yang rong zom chen po yis //
NK131(do)004:284: mdzad pa'i bstan bcos du ma dang //
NK131(do)004:285: kun mkhyen dri med 'od zer gyi //
NK131(do)004:286: mdzod chen bdun sogs rtsa 'grel dang //
NK131(do)004:287: khams dbus gtsang gsum la sogs par //
NK131(do)004:288: rnying ma'i rgyud 'bum mang bzhengs pa'i //
NK131(do)004:289: dkar chag dpe ther so so dang //
NK131(do)004:290: rgyal dbang lnga pa chen po yi //
NK131(do)004:291: gsung 'bum phar chen rnams su yang //
NK131(do)004:292: lung dang rig pa gting zab pas //
NK131(do)004:293: dpyis phyis nyid du sgrub pa yod //
NK131(do)004:294: sngon dus snga 'gyur gzhung nyid la //
NK131(do)004:295: log par rtog nas rgal ba sogs //
NK131(do)004:297: ma rtog the tshom gyis dri ba //
NK131(do)004:298: karma mi bskyod rdo rje dang //
NK131(do)004:299: dgongs gzhi dang ni dgos pa la //
NK131(do)004:300: ltos nas gsar rnying thun mong du //
NK131(do)004:302: khu dbon gnyis kyi 'byams yig dang //
NK131(do)004:305: gzhan yang sa pan bu ston dang //
NK131(do)004:306: pan chen sh+aaka mchog la sogs pas //
NK131(do)004:307: brtag dpyad gzhir mdzad dgag sgrub bcas //
NK131(do)004:308: mang zhig mdzad pa de dag gi //
NK131(do)004:309: lan dang dgongs pa'i gsal byed sogs //
NK131(do)004:310: rim par spros pa rgya ra ba //
NK131(do)004:311: nam mkha' chos kyi rgya mtsho yi //
NK131(do)004:312: rtsod bzlog rdo rje pha lam yod //
NK131(do)004:313: sog bzlog blo gros rgya mtsho yis //
NK131(do)004:314: dpal 'dzin nyid kyi sger lan du //
NK131(do)004:315: rtsod bzlog nges don 'brug sgra dang //
NK131(do)004:316: mi bskyod rdo rje'i chab shog lan //
NK131(do)004:317: dris lan lung rig 'brug sgra yod //
NK131(do)004:318: 'byams yig gsum gyi lan dang ni //
NK131(do)004:319: sa pan bu ston sh+aaka mchog gi //
NK131(do)004:320: dgag sgrub dbye gsal byas pa'ang yod //
NK131(do)004:321: sh+aaka mchog legs bshad gser thur la //
NK131(do)004:322: bya ba chos rje skal bzang pas //
NK131(do)004:323: brgal lan lung rig sgo 'byed springs //
NK131(do)004:324: de'i lan pan chen rang nyid kyis //
NK131(do)004:325: nges don rab gsal ces bya bar //
NK131(do)004:326: rnying ma dgag pa min tshul gyi //
NK131(do)004:327: dag zhus zhib tu phul ba'ang yod //
NK131(do)004:328: smin gling rab 'byams chos grags kyis //
NK131(do)004:329: snga phyi'i rtsod pa thams cad kyi //
NK131(do)004:330: lan gyi phreng ba rgyas pa yod //
NK131(do)004:332: rgya ra ba yi rtsod bzlog la //
NK131(do)004:333: rno brtags rgyas par spros pa dang //
NK131(do)004:334: grub mtha' rab tu dbye ba'i gtam //
NK131(do)004:335: rtog ge'i gnyen po zhes bya dang //
NK131(do)004:337: don gyi mdo 'gag ces bya dang //
NK131(do)004:338: shin tu rnal 'byor grub mtha' bzhir //
NK131(do)004:339: ston pa rdo rje zeg ma dang //
NK131(do)004:340: rdzogs chen lta ba ha shang gi //
NK131(do)004:342: mdzad pa kun mkhyen zhal lung sogs //
NK131(do)004:343: tshad ldan bstan bcos du ma yod //
NK131(do)004:344: mkhas pa'i dbang po kahthoga pa //
NK131(do)004:345: 'gyur med tshe dbang mchog grub kyis //
NK131(do)004:346: sdom gsum rab dbye'i gsal byed du //
NK131(do)004:347: 'du ma byas pa'i gan mdzod dang //
NK131(do)004:348: brag kar dge bshes rtsod lan du //
NK131(do)004:349: spel ba lung gi rnga chen sogs //
NK131(do)004:350: rtsod bzlog bstan bcos mang zhig yod //
NK131(do)004:351: brgal lan rtsod bzlog de rnams su //
NK131(do)004:352: brtags pa gsum sogs tshad ldan gyi //
NK131(do)004:353: lung rig du mas rnam dag tu //
NK131(do)004:354: bsgrubs zin pas na der ltos shig /
NK131(do)004:355: de ltar lung dang rig pa yis //
NK131(do)004:356: rnying ma'i gzhung lugs mtha' dag kun //
NK131(do)004:357: bka' dang bstan bcos rnam dag tu //
NK131(do)004:358: legs par grub par gyur pa na //
NK131(do)004:359: de rjes chu brgya zom 'og dang //
NK131(do)004:361: gzhung brgya rig pa gcig nyid kyis //
NK131(do)004:362: gsal bar grub pa ma yin nam //
NK131(do)004:363: des na rigs drug gnas 'dren dang //
NK131(do)004:364: rigs brgya'i tsaka gdub rab byung gi //
NK131(do)004:365: rnam pa'i lha yis mtshon thogs sogs //
NK131(do)004:366: lam gyi gnad du mi che yang //
NK131(do)004:367: gzhan don phriin las phran tsheg dang //
NK131(do)004:368: phyag bzhes mtshon byed drang don brda' //
NK131(do)004:369: cung zad mi 'dra'i khyad par dag /
NK131(do)004:370: rnying ma'i gzhung las bshad pa med //
NK131(do)004:371: de yang rgyal ba'i bka' yin par //
NK131(do)004:372: rig pa snga mas bsgrubs zin to //
NK131(do)004:373: rnying ma'i gzhung la grags na'ang //
NK131(do)004:374: gsar ma'i rgyud du ma bshad pas //
NK131(do)004:375: de dag 'thad pa min ce na //
NK131(do)004:376: rtags khyab gnyis ka ma grub ste //
NK131(do)004:377: ngan song sbyong ba'i rgyud sogs nas //
NK131(do)004:378: gnas nas drang ba bshad phyir dang //
NK131(do)004:379: ras bris sku gzugs bshad phyir dang //
NK131(do)004:380: mi 'khrugs chag bral sprul sku yis //
NK131(do)004:381: mtshon cha rdo rje thogs phyir do //
NK131(do)004:382: gzhung lugs gcig la grags pa de //
NK131(do)004:383: gcig dang mthun pa'i nges pa med //
NK131(do)004:384: nyan thos pa yi bden pa bzhi //
NK131(do)004:385: mu stegs pa yi lugs la med //
NK131(do)004:386: theg chen pa yi khyad chos rnams //
NK131(do)004:387: nyan thos pa la ma grags shing //
NK131(do)004:388: rdo rje theg pa'i rim pa gnyis //
NK131(do)004:389: phar phyin gzhung du bshad pa med //
NK131(do)004:390: thabs shes rgyud kyi sbyor sgrol sogs //
NK131(do)004:391: phyi rgyud rnams su ma bshad kyang //
NK131(do)004:392: des de log par ga la grub //
NK131(do)004:393: de dang 'di dag mtshungs pas so //
NK131(do)004:394: tsaka gdub dkyil 'khor dod yin par //
NK131(do)004:395: sems pa'ang khyod rang 'khrul par zad //
NK131(do)004:396: chos rje sa skya pan+di tas //
NK131(do)004:397: rab dbye theg dgur dpyad skabs kyi //
NK131(do)004:398: tshig de deng sang sa skya pa //
NK131(do)004:399: mkhas blun kun gyis cal sgrogs su //
NK131(do)004:400: byed mod de yi go ba'i gnad //
NK131(do)004:401: shes pa khyed kyi khrod na dkon //
NK131(do)004:402: de'i don rdzogs pa chen po la //
NK131(do)004:403: rtogs bya'i don dang rtogs byed thabs //
NK131(do)004:404: rnam pa gnyis su dbye ba la //
NK131(do)004:405: rtogs bya don gyi rdzogs chen ni //
NK131(do)004:406: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes te //
NK131(do)004:407: dmigs med brjod pa dang bral ba //
NK131(do)004:408: de yi ngo bo'i rang ldog nas //
NK131(do)004:409: ming tshig yi ge dang bral phyir //
NK131(do)004:410: brjod byed tshig gi theg pa ru //
NK131(do)004:411: bzhag pa mkhas pa min zhes gsungs //
NK131(do)004:412: de rtogs pa yi thabs la ni //
NK131(do)004:413: theg pa'i rim pa yod pa yin //
NK131(do)004:414: ces pas rtog byed thabs kyi ni //
NK131(do)004:415: theg rim dgu po shugs kyis bstan //
NK131(do)004:416: 'on kyang gsang sngags gsar ma la //
NK131(do)004:417: rnal 'byor chen po'i ltag na ni //
NK131(do)004:418: de bas mtho ba'i rgyud sde med //
NK131(do)004:419: sgom pa'i dmigs pa nyid kyang ni //
NK131(do)004:420: rnal 'byor chen po'i ltag na med //
NK131(do)004:421: ces pas theg rim gong ma gnyis //
NK131(do)004:422: gsar ma pa la med pa yi //
NK131(do)004:423: rnam bcad dngos su bstan pa yis //
NK131(do)004:424: de gnyis rnying ma'i khyad chos su //
NK131(do)004:425: yod pa'i yongs gcod shugs las bstan //
NK131(do)004:426: rnying ma'i lugs la theg pa dgu //
NK131(do)004:427: yod pa'i zhal bzhes gzhung 'di dang //
NK131(do)004:428: thub dgongs sogs su yang yang mdzad //
NK131(do)004:429: de ltar rnam dbye legs phyes nas //
NK131(do)004:430: smras na dam pa'i dgongs pa bsal //
NK131(do)004:431: gzhan du a ti yo ga nyid //
NK131(do)004:432: ye shes yin par bzhed pa la //
NK131(do)004:433: theg pa yin par spyir bkag ces //
NK131(do)004:434: khyed cag de ltar smra na ni //
NK131(do)004:435: rgyan dang theg pa sdud pa la sogs pa'i //
NK131(do)004:436: gzhung lugs kun dang dga' ba'i phyir //
NK131(do)004:437: tsan+dana sol bar byas pa bzhin //
NK131(do)004:438: mkhas pa'i legs bshad blo skyon gyis //
NK131(do)004:439: dri ma can du ma byas sam //
NK131(do)004:441: rgyud lung man ngag gsum sbyar zhing //
NK131(do)004:442: rig pas 'thad par bsgrub pa yis //
NK131(do)004:443: yid ches nges shes 'dren nus pa'i //
NK131(do)004:444: shes byed dam pa'i zhal gyi lung //
NK131(do)004:445: mchis mod de dag shes 'dod na //
NK131(do)004:446: rgyud sde'i zab gnad 'chad dgos pas //
NK131(do)004:447: rgyud nas bshad pa'i 'chad nyan gyi //
NK131(do)004:448: tshul rnams ji bzhin sgrub dgos kyi //
NK131(do)004:449: co 'dri rtsed mo'i rtsod len du //
NK131(do)004:450: zab don gsang ba su zhig sgrogs //
NK131(do)004:452: gsar ma'i dus su byon pa yi //
NK131(do)004:453: lha cig jo bo chen po dang //
NK131(do)004:455: dam pa sangs rgyas la sogs pa'i //
NK131(do)004:456: rgya gar grub thob mang po dang //
NK131(do)004:457: 'gos lo gzhon nu dpal ba dang //
NK131(do)004:458: thar lo nyi ma rgyal mtshan dang //
NK131(do)004:459: 'bri gung rin chen dpal bzang po //
NK131(do)004:460: rig ral jo nang kun mkhyen pa //
NK131(do)004:461: grub thob o rgyan pa dang ni //
NK131(do)004:462: kun mkhyen tsong kha pa sogs kyi //
NK131(do)004:463: mchog gzigs du mas rnam dag tu //
NK131(do)004:464: zhal zhes basngagasa brjod mdzad pa mang //
NK131(do)004:466: smod par byed pa snying rje'i gnas //
NK131(do)004:467: de tsam du yang ma zad de //
NK131(do)004:468: grub pa thob pa'i lag rjes su //
NK131(do)004:469: sngon byon rje 'bangs nyer lnga dang //
NK131(do)004:470: bar du so zur gnubs dang gnyags //
NK131(do)004:471: slob rgyud nam mkha'i skar tshogs tsam //
NK131(do)004:472: phyis byon nyang ral chos dbang dang //
NK131(do)004:473: gling pa brgyad sogs gter ston dang //
NK131(do)004:474: kahdapala rdzogs chen grub thob rnams //
NK131(do)004:475: phung po 'od skur yal ba dang //
NK131(do)004:477: gdung dang ring bsrel bzhag nas kyang //
NK131(do)004:478: sgra 'od me tog char dang bcas //
NK131(do)004:479: rang bzhin sprul pa'i zhing rnams su //
NK131(do)004:480: phebs pa'i gang zag bgrang las 'das //
NK131(do)004:481: grol rtags de 'dra mngon sum du //
NK131(do)004:482: 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan nyams len chos //
NK131(do)004:483: snga 'gyur yo ga sde gsum po //
NK131(do)004:484: rgyal ba rdo rje 'chang chen gyi //
NK131(do)004:485: nye lam zab mo yin phyir dang //
NK131(do)004:486: de la dam nyams bka' rkun gyis //
NK131(do)004:487: rang bzos bslad pa ma zhugs dang //
NK131(do)004:488: rdo rje 'chang nas da lta'i par //
NK131(do)004:489: byin rlabs brgyud pa ma chad pa'i //
NK131(do)004:490: rtags su mngon sum tshad ma'o //
NK131(do)004:491: de phyir tshad ma du ma yis //
NK131(do)004:492: tshad mar grub pa'i lam de la //
NK131(do)004:493: tshad ma nyid du bzung byas na //
NK131(do)004:494: gang zag nyid kyang tshad mar 'gro //
NK131(do)004:496: rtsod yig dri tshig spel ba'i rgyu //
NK131(do)004:497: kun slong 'dra min mang yod kyang //
NK131(do)004:498: brtags na rnam pa gsum du nges //
NK131(do)004:499: blo chung grags pa don gnyer dang //
NK131(do)004:500: snying nas chos la sdang ba dang //
NK131(do)004:501: rnam dag chos la sgro skur gyi //
NK131(do)004:503: gal te grangs pa don gnyer na //
NK131(do)004:504: grags skam snying po ma mchis kyang //
NK131(do)004:505: dam pa'i rnam thar gzhan dag gis //
NK131(do)004:506: sgrub dang 'phral phug kun tu dge //
NK131(do)004:507: chos dang chos min 'byed do lo'i //
NK131(do)004:508: chos spongs las kyi sgrib pa 'dis //
NK131(do)004:509: grags pa sgrub pa ya nga'i gnas //
NK131(do)004:510: khe las nye che spangs na legs //
NK131(do)004:511: zhes nas chos la sdang yin na //
NK131(do)004:512: chos la sdang ba'i gang zag la //
NK131(do)004:513: thar lam med par thub pas gsung //
NK131(do)004:514: des na yang dag lung rig gi //
NK131(do)004:515: thugs rje'i dbyangs thag la brten nas //
NK131(do)004:516: thar ba'i lam du zhugs na legs //
NK131(do)004:517: cis kyang mi ldog smod na ni //
NK131(do)004:518: smyon pa'i rjes su long ba bzhin //
NK131(do)004:519: lha sbyin dang ni dpal 'dzin gyi //
NK131(do)004:520: rjes la tsham tshom med pa ru //
NK131(do)004:521: mchong ba sngon gyi las yin pas //
NK131(do)004:522: rgyal ba'i phyag gis mi khog na //
NK131(do)004:523: bdag dang bdag 'dras ci zhig bya //
NK131(do)004:524: khyod la sdig par ma gyur ces //
NK131(do)004:525: lhag pa'i bsam pa'i smon lam 'debs //
NK131(do)004:526: the tshom gcod par 'dod na ni //
NK131(do)004:527: gong du bshad pa'i rtsod lan ni //
NK131(do)004:528: yig cha de dag rnams dang ni //
NK131(do)004:529: rnying ma'i gzhung lugs mtha' dag la //
NK131(do)004:530: shes rab gsum gyi mig sgrubs dang //
NK131(do)004:531: som nyi'i gnas kun ldog pa yod //
NK131(do)004:532: gal te de ltar brtag pa na //
NK131(do)004:533: rgyal ba'i bka' lung dang 'gal zhing //
NK131(do)004:534: gtan tshigs rgya yis ma thebs pas //
NK131(do)004:535: 'grel pa bstan bcos ji snyed du //
NK131(do)004:536: dgag bzhag spang gsum ma nus shing //
NK131(do)004:537: rtsod lan rnams su lung rig gis //
NK131(do)004:538: legs par grub par ma gyur pas //
NK131(do)004:539: yang dag lam du the tshom pa'i //
NK131(do)004:540: gnas shig khyod la mngon gyur na //
NK131(do)004:542: grong tshig kha shas tsam min par //
NK131(do)004:543: spyir btang dmigs gsal rdzas ldog dang //
NK131(do)004:544: sel dang sgrub pa skabs phyed pa'i //
NK131(do)004:545: brgal brtags mkhas pas dpyad 'os par //
NK131(do)004:546: sgrub par gyis dang de'i dus su //
NK131(do)004:547: dpal ldan chos kyi grags pa yi //
NK131(do)004:548: gzhung dang mthun pa'i lung rig gi //
NK131(do)004:550: de las gzhan du snga 'gyur gyi //
NK131(do)004:551: gzhung lugs rnam dag ma mthong bzhin //
NK131(do)004:552: blo gros rtsing po dpyad pa'i gtam //
NK131(do)004:553: hol rgyug byed pa dpyad 'os min //
NK131(do)004:555: dkyus sa ma brtan rta rgyug dang //
NK131(do)004:556: phyogs snga ma nges rtsod pa gsum //
NK131(do)004:557: dpyod ldan rnams kyi khrel ba'i gnas //
NK131(do)004:558: kye ma deng sang snyigs ma'i gnas skabs 'dir //
NK131(do)004:559: rtog ge zol mas thub bstan dkrugs pas skyo //
NK131(do)004:560: 'byung bya mun pa'i smag la dgod mod kyi //
NK131(do)004:561: nyin mo h+aum sgra sgrogs na ltas ngan yin //
NK131(do)004:562: dpang gyur mkhas pa'i skye bo zad pa na //
NK131(do)004:563: blun pos bab col sgrogs pa chos nyid kyang //
NK131(do)004:564: bstan 'dzin nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor bkrag 'bar zhing //
NK131(do)004:565: bshad sgrub 'od kyis phyogs kun khyab dus 'dir //
NK131(do)004:566: 'gal 'du'i rang bzhin gnag rdzi'i gtam zangs ma //
NK131(do)004:567: 'dzem med gcer rgyug byed pa e ma mtshar //
NK131(do)004:568: deng 'dir log rtog mun pa sun 'byin pa'i //
NK131(do)004:569: brgal lan skya rengs dang po spros zin gyis //
NK131(do)004:570: ma brtags mu cor smra rnams bag yod mdzod //
NK131(do)004:571: phyis nas lung rig nyin byed 'char ta re //
NK131(do)004:572: de skad yongs rdzogs bstan pa'i mnga' bdag che //
NK131(do)004:573: mdo khams grub pa'i dbang phyug rdzogs chen pa'i //
NK131(do)004:574: bka' 'babs yongs kyi tha shal snyoms las pa //
NK131(do)004:575: skyes thob sbyangs pa'i blo gros na phra yang //
NK131(do)004:576: rang gzhan grub mtha' rgya mtsho'i mtha' son pa'i //
NK131(do)004:577: smra ba'i nyi ma rgyal sras chos rje dang //
NK131(do)004:578: gtsug lag sgo brgya 'byed la zla bral ba'i //
NK131(do)004:579: gzhon nu 'jigs med chos kyi dbang po sogs //
NK131(do)004:580: yongs 'dzin mkhas dbang du ma'i zhabs kyi rdul //
NK131(do)004:581: spyi bor son pa'i mthu las legs bshad gtam //
NK131(do)004:582: cung zad sma la dbang pa'i klog pa ba //
NK131(do)004:583: pad+ma badz+ra zhes byar 'bod pa des //
NK131(do)004:584: don gnyer can 'gas nan gyis bskul ba'i ngor //
NK131(do)004:585: ru dam dpal gyi gtsug lag khang chen po'i //
NK131(do)004:586: nye gam bsam gtan sgom pa'i khang bu nas //
NK131(do)004:587: thun mtshams gsum du shar mar bris nas springs //
NK131(do)004:588: de las byung ba'i dge tshogs gangs ri'i tog /
NK131(do)004:589: ston zla'i 'od zer 'khyud ltar dkar ba des //
NK131(do)004:590: rang gzhan the tshom mun pa kun bsal nas //
NK131(do)004:591: chos rab rnam 'byed blo gros 'phel gyur cig /
NK131(do)004:592: ces pa'ang bgro gleng pa bsod nams bstan pas bris
